sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) 
FROM measurement_imports 
WHERE import_status = 'success';

external_knowledge:
Popularity refers to how often a measurement is accessed, indicated by the access count; 
A lower access rank means lower popularity; 
Sepal dimensions and petal dimensions refer to the length and width of the sepal and petal in centimeters, respectively; 
Collector's name refers to the user who collected the measurement; 
Species, genus, and family refer to the classification of the plant species.
